@swap・10 **Quick announcement for testnet participants** - a patch was just pushed for a bug that was sort of breaking the reward system. We've also temporarily changed the scoring period parameters to decrease the scoring period lengths. The scoring periods for challenge requests are now between the range of 1.5hrs-3hrs (vs. 2-12hrs which is what is was previously). This should allow us to make more frequent observations about how the reward system is performing. Please do note that these parameters will be changed back to what they were previously shortly before we launch 2.0.0 on mainnet.

Happy mining ⛏️  and validating 🔍

